coretest.auxiliary

Class CodeRepresentationMaps

  • java.lang.Object
    • coretest.auxiliary.CodeRepresentationMaps

  • public class CodeRepresentationMaps
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides methods creating maps, which contain all CodePackages and CodeElements referenced with their name for easier testing. The methods creating these maps are tested within this class as well.
    Author:
    dschoenicke
